sentence: Washington Republican Rep. Jaime Herrera-Beutler also topped a half-million dollars, more than the $300,000 raised by Trump-backed challenger Joe Kent.
author: Cameron Joseph
title: Trump's Favorite Candidates Are Getting Crushed in Fundraising
